Den Bussche (2003), Hughes et al. (2014), Isaac et al. (2007), Koopman (1993, 1994), Koopman &amp; Jones (1970), Nowak (1999), Roehrs et al. (2010), Simmons (2005), Tate (1941e, 1942b), Thomas (1897b, 1914c), Volleth &amp; Tidemann (1991).
